OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,FThe mother of Thames Valley police
OL,7,Fofficer Andrew Harper has said the
OL,8,Ffact that two of his killers are being
OL,9,Fconsidered for early release is
OL,10,F"another letdown" for her son.
OL,12,FIt comes after the constable's widow
OL,13,FLissie Harper criticised the early
OL,14,Frelease scheme as "deplorable".
OL,16,FPc Harper was 28 years old when he
OL,17,Fsustained fatal injuries while
OL,18,Fresponding to a quad bike theft in
OL,19,FSulhamstead, Berkshire, in August 2019.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@QO]vD@SOUvD@^O]
