OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,FThe driver of the vehicle which caused
OL,7,FPc Harper's death, Henry Long,
OL,8,Freceived a 16-year sentence, and will
OL,9,Fnot be eligible for the scheme.
OL,11,FBut early release could be on the
OL,12,Fcards for Jessie Cole and Albert
OL,13,FBowers, who were passengers in the car
OL,14,Fand handed 13 years in custody for
OL,15,Fmanslaughter after a trial at the Old
OL,16,FBailey in 2020.
OL,18,FBoth men might now be eligible to be
OL,19,Freleased from prison after serving
OL,20,Fhalf of their sentences, rather than
OL,21,Ftwo-thirds.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,FUnder the new Sentencing Act, set to
OL,7,Fcome into force in September, some
OL,8,F6,000 criminals are set to be released
OL,9,Funder the early prison release scheme.
OL,11,FAsked about how the family feel about
OL,12,Fthe potential release, Pc Harper's
OL,13,Fmother Debbie Adlam told BBC Radio 4's
OL,14,FToday programme: "It just feels like
OL,15,Fanother letdown for Andrew, really.
OL,17,F"You know, when you look at the
OL,18,Fhorrific way he was killed, we have to
OL,19,Flive with that, we have to know, you
OL,20,Fknow, that we've still got to live a
OL,21,Flife.
OL,26,@vD@ROUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,F"We've got to do our best to do a life
OL,7,Fas best we can for him and in his
OL,8,Fname, really."
OL,10,FShe urged Prime Minister Andy Burnham
OL,11,Fto "look at the big picture" and said
OL,12,Fthe justice system "needs a proper
OL,13,Foverhaul".
OL,15,FMr Burnham has said he will review the
OL,16,Fearly release policy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@NO]sD@DOUsD@\O]tD@TOUuD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
