OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,F"I can't say that I can change the
OL,7,Fpolicy completely, but I will look at
OL,8,Fit in detail before we go further
OL,9,Fforward," he told reporters on
OL,10,FWednesday.
OL,12,FOne of his ministers said the prime
OL,13,Fminister is looking at the
OL,14,F"implementation" of the scheme.
OL,16,FAsked if that means it might not
OL,17,Fhappen, Chief Secretary to the
OL,18,FTreasury Emma Reynolds told the BBC:
OL,19,F"That is something that he and the
OL,20,FJustice Secretary will set out in the
OL,21,Fcoming weeks."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]vD@AOUvD@PO]{D@AOU}D@NO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
