OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,FMs Adlam said the justice system needs
OL,7,Fa "proper overhaul".
OL,9,F"Just saying we'll release them to
OL,10,Frelieve the pressure is actually
OL,11,Fbottling up problems for the future.
OL,13,F"You know, these people aren't just
OL,14,Fgoing to go away and live a nice life.
OL,16,F"Some will, some will have learnt
OL,17,Ftheir lesson, but as we know, the
OL,18,Freoffending rates are so high.
OL,26,@oD@COUoD@SO]qD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
