OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,382,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1784810903
OL,3,CMother of Pc Harper says early release
OL,4,Cof killers 'another letdown for Andrew'
OL,6,F"You know, the consequences of this,
OL,7,Fthey need to look at the bigger
OL,8,Fpicture."
OL,10,FPc Harper's widow Lissie said in a
OL,11,Frare statement on Wednesday: "It is
OL,12,Fdeplorable to me that we have reached
OL,13,Fa point where releasing prisoners
OL,14,Fearly is even considered acceptable.
OL,16,F"We speak of justice, accountability
OL,17,Fand standing with victims, yet
OL,18,Fdecisions like this do the opposite."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]sD@^OUxD@AOUzD@eO]
